<i>adverb</i>: 알뜰히 [알뜰히], 살뜰히 [살뜰히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>알뜰히 [알뜰히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. frugally; thriftily</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 살림을 규모 있고 계획성 있게 하여 빈틈이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of keeping the finance of one's household or business well planned and managed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. warmly; tenderly; deeply</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 아끼고 위하는 마음이 진실하고 지극하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With sincere and faithful mind in treating someone kindly.</dd><br>
<dt>살뜰히 [살뜰히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sincerely; kindly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 행동이 정성스럽고 친절하며 다정하게.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one thinking or acting sincerely, kindly and affectionately.</dd><br>
<dd>2. meticulously; frugally</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 살림을 착실하고 실속 있게 하여 빈틈이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one doing a job or house chores dutifully and thoroughly, without wasting resources.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>